Day 15 – Monitoring EC2 and Docker Container

Commands
- List containers: `docker ps`
- View logs: `docker logs <container_id>`
- CPU & memory usage: `top` or `htop`
- Free memory: `free -h`
- Disk usage: `df -h`

Outcome
▫️Able to check ML API container logs  
▫️Monitor EC2 resources (CPU, memory, disk)  
▫️Ensured ML API is healthy
